: formula_3

Restriction 1: formula_69 is a variable which does not occur in formula_2.

Restriction 2: There is no occurrence, free or bound, of formula_69 in formula_3.

Restriction 3: formula_69 is not mentioned in any hypothesis or undischarged assumptions.

==Rules of substructural logic==
The following are special cases of universal generalization and existential elimination; these occur in substructural logics, such as linear logic.
;Rule of weakening (or monotonicity of entailment) (aka no-cloning theorem)

