* Portrayed by Pran in the 1956 Indian film &quot;Halaku&quot;.
* Portrayed by Öztürk Serengil in &quot;Cengiz Han&#x27;ın Hazineleri&quot; (1962)
* Portrayed by Zhang Jingda and Zhang Bolun in &quot;The Legend of Kublai Khan&quot; (2013)

